        },
        {
          "sentence": "Following a government meeting at the House of Culture, Robert Fico was greeting a crowd in the square and shaking hands with citizens",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "A man in the crowd yelled for Fico to approach and shot him at close range with a handgun",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "The alleged assailant was immediately detained by Fico's bodyguards and police cordoned off the area",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.novinky.cz/clanek/zahranicni-evropa-video-zachytilo-jak-policie-zpacifikovala-atentatnika-po-strelbe-na-fica-40471872"
