          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "An interior ministry official said Fico was conscious while being transported",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Five shots were fired from a handgun, with two shots striking Fico in his abdomen and one in his shoulder,  leaving him in a life-threatening condition",
